(3206, 742, '_yoast_wpseo_opengraph-title', 'Ben Erwin will be moderating a panel on Spatial Computing'),
(3207, 742, '_yoast_wpseo_opengraph-description', 'Volumetric Content is the next major evolution in media. It captures real depth which is rendered as holograms in Light-field displays and Virtual, Augmented, and Mixed Reality headsets. The Spatial Computing technology used to create video games and special effects for movies allows Six Degrees of Freedom to move within and around virtual environments and objects, where you get to be the camera. This is industry-changing as a collaborative platform; with wide-ranging enterprise use-cases in education, health, manufacturing, travel, architecture, and real estate as well as journalism, sports, gaming and entertainment for consumers. This panel will explore how the multi-billion dollar XR space will create unprecedented opportunity using the full stack of World 4.0 technologies.'),
