(33, 1, '2018-10-03 22:17:20', '2018-10-03 22:17:20', 'This Year, the Silicon Harlem annual conference examines how emerging technologies will profoundly change every aspect of our lives the way that the internet changed the way we communicate. They\'re calling it the Fourth Industrial Revolution and will change Education, Finance, Content, Community, Security and Business forever.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nArtificial Intelligence Machine Learning, Robotics, 3D Printing\r\nInternet of Things, Smart Everything, Sensors, Drones,\r\nBlockchain  Digital Currency Smart Contracts Cloud\r\nVirtual Reality, Augmented Reality, Mixed Reality', 'RE<>THINK EVERYTHING', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '15-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-03 22:17:20', '2018-10-03 22:17:20', '', 15, 'http://siliconharlemconf.192.168.1.11.xip.io:8886/2018/10/03/15-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
