(229, 3, '2018-10-15 15:01:48', '2018-10-15 15:01:48', 'Chirag Shah is the Founder of Lifestyle Westchester; the fastest growing media company online in Westchester County New York. Lifestyle Westchester focuses on our community, people and experiences within it. In 18 months, Lifestyle Westchester has gained over 20,000 followers on Social Media; had over 300,000 people watch videos on the community and has an average of 100 hours a month watched on our Facebook page. He is also the owner of Life NY Real Estate. Chirag is the Vice President for the Hudson Gateway Multiple Listing Service, serves on the Board of Directors for the Hudson Gateway MLS, and is the Chair of the Young Professionals Network. He has been a featured speaker on the use of technology at Triple Play National Convention, National Association of Realtors Tech Edge, New York State Association of Realtors Fall Business Meetings, Long Island Multiple Listing Service Tech Fair, and Hudson Gateway Association of Realtors Members Day.  He recently was appointed to serve on the Westchester County Executive MWBE Task Force. He has many awards including being recognized in the 40 Under 40 rising stars by the Business Council in Westchester. Chirag is a recent graduate of the Leadership Westchester Program. He is married with two children and lives in Westchester County.\r\n', 'Chirag Shah', 'Chirag Shah is the Founder of Lifestyle Westchester; the fastest growing media company online in Westchester County New York. Lifestyle Westchester focuses on our community, people and experiences within it. In 18 months, Lifestyle Westchester has gained over 20,000 followers on Social Media; had over 300,000 people watch videos on the community and has an average of 100 hours a month watched on our Facebook page.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'chirag-shah', '', '', '2018-10-22 23:41:51', '2018-10-22 23:41:51', '', 411, 'http://conference.siliconharlem.net/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=229', 397, 'speaker', '', 0),
