(435, 1, '2019-08-05 05:48:59', '2019-08-05 05:48:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>World 4.0 - Let’s Get Ready!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Economic Opportunity and the 4th Industrial Revolution<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Friday, October 18th at the National Black Theater, Silicon Harlem will convene luminary thought leaders across the spectrum of new technologies that will power our future. Our 6th Annual Next-Gen Tech Conference will think forward to life in New York City in 2050 and the opportunities being created by advanced science.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Get in front of the coming transformations that will reshape our communities, our cities and our world. Changes to our society that are already underway cannot be underestimated. The impact on education, health, finance, transportation, civics, employment and urban living will be profound. Catch the buzz, parse the hype and learn the lingo of World 4.0 at Silicon Harlem’s biggest event yet.&nbsp;<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Panel discussion topics include Artificial Intelligence, 5G, IoT, Blockchain, Extended Reality, Bio-tech, Data, and Cities of Tomorrow. Consider how the 4th Industrial Revolution will affect your career, your family and your future. Since 2013, Silicon Harlem has been dedicated Upper Manhattan a stakeholder in the urban economic engine of the future.&nbsp; Join us for the networking opportunity of the year.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Let’s Get Ready!</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The 6th Annual Conference opens with the theme of preparedness. What is New York City doing to attract the jobs of the future? How is the Harlem Community preparing for the 4th Industrial Revolution and where do you fit in? Special Guests will talk about what’s changing and where the opportunities are going to be in the coming decade.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Agenda', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '414-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-05 05:48:59', '2019-08-05 05:48:59', '', 414, 'http://siliconharlemconf:8886/2019/08/05/414-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
