(748, 1, '2019-08-19 15:29:51', '2019-08-19 15:29:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Economic Opportunity and the 4th Industrial Revolution</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On Friday, October 18th at the National Black Theater, Silicon Harlem will convene luminary thought leaders of the new technologies that will power our future. At our Annual Next-Gen Tech Conference we will think forward to life in New York City in 2050 and the economic opportunities being created by looking at Community as a Platform. Get in front of the coming transformations that will reshape our world. The impact on education, health, finance, transportation, civics, employment and urban living will be profound. Catch the buzz, parse the hype and learn the lingo of World 4.0 at Silicon Harlem’s biggest event yet.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Panel discussion topics will include Artificial Intelligence, 5G, IoT, Blockchain, Extended Reality, Bio-tech, Quantum Computing, and Cities of Tomorrow. Learn and consider how the 4th Industrial Revolution will impact your family, your career and your future. Since 2013, Silicon Harlem has been dedicated in providing research, strategies and tools to insure that Upper Manhattan is positioned as an urban economic engine of the future.&nbsp; Join us for the networking opportunity of the year.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><strong>World 4.0: Let’s Get Ready!</strong></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The 6th Annual Conference opens with the theme of preparedness. What is New York City doing to attract the jobs of the future? How is the Harlem Community preparing for the 4th Industrial Revolution and where do you fit in? Special Guests will talk about what’s changing and where the opportunities are going to be in the coming decade.<br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Agenda', 'Join us as we explore the vast  economic opportunities of the 4th Industrial Revolution.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '414-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-19 15:29:51', '2019-08-19 15:29:51', '', 414, 'http://siliconharlemconf:8886/2019/08/19/414-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
