(755, 1, '2019-08-20 17:11:00', '2019-08-20 17:11:00', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Silicon Harlem will hold this year’s 6<sup>th</sup> Annual Next Gen Tech Conference at the</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>National Black Theater on Friday, October 18<sup>th</sup>. This year’s conference theme is</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“World 4.0: Let’s Get Ready!”&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This year’s conference will build upon last year’s theme of the humanization of AI, Block Chain, Machine Learning, Driverless Cars, AR, VR and Smart Cities and extrapolate from there to provide the audience with an inclusive vision of the world as it undergoes profound change driven by the oncoming of the Fourth Industrial Revolution.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our overarching questions that will propel us forward throughout the day are:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>· &nbsp; 	How do I get a grasp on such profound material change?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>· &nbsp; 	What should I do to prepare to take advantage of these once-in-a-lifetime transformations?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>· &nbsp; 	What is being done both on the public institutional level and the level of the civic polity to ensure that we as citizens experience a positive transition into this new age?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>· &nbsp; 	From the standpoint of my family, how will this affect us from a multi-generational point-of-view?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our objective is to make sure that Harlem, Upper Manhattan and it’s kindred communities both in and outside NYC are platformed so that they can leapfrog and take full advantage of the socio-economic opportunities that the next industrial revolution will create.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":740} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"http://siliconharlemconf:8886/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/4IR-white-01.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-740\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>The 4</strong><strong><sup>th</sup></strong><strong> Industrial Revolution: A Brief Primer</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The First Industrial Revolution used water and steam power to mechanize production. The Second used electric power to create mass production. The Third used electronics and information technology to automate production. Now a <br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Agenda', 'Join us as we explore the vast  economic opportunities of the 4th Industrial Revolution.', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '414-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-20 17:11:00', '2019-08-20 17:11:00', '', 414, 'http://siliconharlemconf:8886/2019/08/20/414-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
