(874, 0, '2019-10-02 14:14:23', '2019-10-02 14:14:23', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ty is the Global Lead, The B2B Institute @LinkedIn, the former President of LinkedIn\'s Black Inclusion Group (BIG) and Co-Founder of TransformHER. Ty is passionate about connecting people with information needed to make intelligent decisions, delivering educational content to help marketers stay on top of the latest in digital marketing strategy with a bit of humor. Ty teaches B2B marketing, inbound marketing strategy, account based marketing, social selling, content marketing as well as leadership, diversity and inclusion. Ty is also author of \"Marketers of Tomorrow: A Step by Step Toolkit for Inbound Marketing\".</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Ty Heath', 'Ty is the Global Lead, The B2B Institute @LinkedIn, the former President of LinkedIn\'s Black Inclusion Group (BIG) and Co-Founder of TransformHER. Ty is passionate about connecting people with information needed to make intelligent decisions, delivering educational content to help marketers stay on top of the latest in digital marketing strategy with a bit of humor.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ty-heath', '', '', '2019-10-16 21:23:54', '2019-10-16 21:23:54', '', 410, 'https://conference.siliconharlem.com/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=874', 102, 'speaker', '', 0),
