(885, 0, '2019-10-04 15:28:26', '2019-10-04 15:28:26', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Scott Wang is the business development manager of the Asian American Business Development Center where he assists U.S. and Chinese organizations, businesses and local governments in developing relationships with a focus on investment, tourism, education, and manufacturing. The AABDC is also a leader in Diversity &amp; Inclusion initiatives and programs supporting Asian American business owners, entrepreneurs, and corporate executives. Through AABDC’s effort to promote the Asian American business community, Scott has collaborated with companies like JPMorgan Chase, MGM Resorts, Microsoft, Hennessy, Colgate Palmolive, Diageo and more to create frequent speaker series and private events while continuing to scale AABDC’s annual programs such the Asian American Business Roundtable Summit and the Outstanding 50 Asian Americans in Business Award Gala. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Scott Wang', 'Scott Wang is the business development manager of the Asian American Business Development Center where he assists U.S. and Chinese organizations, businesses and local governments in developing relationships with a focus on investment, tourism, education, and manufacturing.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'scott-wang', '', '', '2019-10-07 20:59:12', '2019-10-07 20:59:12', '', 410, 'https://conference.siliconharlem.com/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=885', 229, 'speaker', '', 0),
