(969, 0, '2019-10-11 19:43:42', '2019-10-11 19:43:42', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>CEO\n&amp; Founder with Over 20 years experience in tech and logistics sectors. As a\nveteran in the logistics industry, Jean identified the need for a technology\nsolution leading to the launch of Brilliant Move Inc, providing a technology\nplatform that offers web-like retail experience with real-time delivery\nsolution experienced in a brick-and-mortar environment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Jean Brilliant', 'CEO & Founder with Over 20 years experience in tech and logistics sectors. As a veteran in the logistics industry, Jean identified the need for a technology solution leading to the launch of Brilliant Move Inc, providing a technology platform that offers web-like retail experience with real-time delivery solution experienced in a brick-and-mortar environment.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jean-brilliant', '', '', '2019-10-11 19:44:50', '2019-10-11 19:44:50', '', 410, 'http://siliconharlemconf.192.168.1.11.xip.io:8886/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=969', 285, 'speaker', '', 0),
